highlights.text: “Llevadme a mi Extremadura” by Sanguijuelas del Guadiana is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Spain, up 16 spots at #75.
“Si Me Necesitas, Llámame” by Siloé has been on Viral Songs Spain the longest, at 113 days straight.
Fernandezz has the most spots on Viral Songs Spain. “Do You Remember” is the highest at #13.
“akatsuki” by 7loseey and Usernam3 is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Spain at #4.
